<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>3. FileLog Setup on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/2-advanced-collector-old/3-filelog/</link><description>Recent content in 3. FileLog Setup on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/2-advanced-collector-old/3-filelog/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>3.1 Configuration</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/2-advanced-collector-old/3-filelog/3-1-configuration/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/2-advanced-collector-old/3-filelog/3-1-configuration/</guid><description>&lt;div class="callout callout--success"&gt;&lt;span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Exercise&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="callout__body"&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the &lt;strong&gt;Agent terminal&lt;/strong&gt; window edit the &lt;code&gt;agent.yaml&lt;/code&gt; and configure the FileLog receiver.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Configure FileLog Receiver&lt;/strong&gt;: The &lt;code&gt;filelog&lt;/code&gt; receiver reads log data from a file and includes custom resource attributes in the log data:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;yaml&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;filelog/quotes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# Receiver Type/Name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;include&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;./quotes.log &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# The file to read log data from&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;include_file_path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kc"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# Include file path in the log data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;include_file_name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kc"&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# Exclude file name from the log data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;resource&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# Add custom resource attributes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;com.splunk.source&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;./quotes.log &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# Source of the log data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;com.splunk.sourcetype&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;quotes &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# Source type of the log data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update &lt;code&gt;logs&lt;/code&gt; pipeline&lt;/strong&gt;: Add the&lt;code&gt;filelog/quotes&lt;/code&gt; receiver to the &lt;code&gt;logs&lt;/code&gt; pipeline only:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>3.2 Test FileLog Receiver</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/2-advanced-collector-old/3-filelog/3-2-test-filelog/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/2-advanced-collector-old/3-filelog/3-2-test-filelog/</guid><description>&lt;div class="callout callout--success"&gt;&lt;span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Exercise&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="callout__body"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Start the Gateway&lt;/strong&gt;: In your &lt;strong&gt;Gateway terminal&lt;/strong&gt; window start the &lt;code&gt;gateway&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Start the Agent&lt;/strong&gt;: In your &lt;strong&gt;Agent terminal&lt;/strong&gt; window start the &lt;code&gt;agent&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A continuous stream of log data from the &lt;code&gt;quotes.log&lt;/code&gt; will be in the &lt;code&gt;agent&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;gateway&lt;/code&gt; debug logs:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;text&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;Timestamp: 1970-01-01 00:00:00 +0000 UTC
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;SeverityText:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;SeverityNumber: Unspecified(0)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;Body: Str(2025-03-06 15:18:32 [ERROR] - There is some good in this world, and it&amp;#39;s worth fighting for. LOTR)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;Attributes:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -&amp;gt; log.file.path: Str(quotes.log)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;Trace ID:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;Span ID:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;Flags: 0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;LogRecord #1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stop the &lt;code&gt;loadgen&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: In the &lt;strong&gt;Logs terminal&lt;/strong&gt; window, stop the &lt;code&gt;loadgen&lt;/code&gt; using &lt;code&gt;Ctrl-C&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>